%p#notice= notice
%h1 Stories
.jumbotron.text-center.bg-white
  %h1 Blog Post Application using Ruby-On-Rails !!
  %p.lead Guide you step by step learning Ruby on Rails through building a Blog application.
  %br/
  %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg{:href => "#", :role => "button", :target => "_blank"} Learn more
%table.table.table-hover
  %thead
    %tr
      %th Title
      %th Content
      %th Action
  %tbody
    - @paginatable_array.each do |story|
      %tr
        %td
          = story[:title]
        %td
          = story[:content]
        %td
          = link_to "Show", story_path(id: @id, title: story[:title]), class: "btn btn-primary"
%br/
= paginate @paginatable_array, theme: 'bootstrap4'
Params Page:
= params[:page]
